title: Yaya Bey performs "end of the world" & more Live on KEXP

author: KEXP
description:
http://KEXP.ORG presents Yaya Bey performing live in the KEXP studio. Recorded September 23, 2025.

Songs:  
end of the world 00:24
in a circle 03:16
exodus the north star 05:57
